    <p>{`The VGW advertises the IP ranges of the VPC which is attached via BGP advertisement to your VPN termination endpoint. VGW uses BGP over TCP port 179 (the standard BGP port) and supports BGP configuration options, like Autonomous System (AS) prepends and Multi-Exit Discriminator (MED).`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "path-selection-after-route-propagation"
